Package com.app.converter.single

Interface Converter<T,U>

Type Parameters:
T - the source type (entity)
U - the target type (model)
All Known Implementing Classes:
ClientConverterImpl, OrderConverterImpl, ProductConverterImpl
public interface Converter<T,U>
A generic interface for converting between two types: an entity and a model.

This interface defines methods to convert an object of type T to an object of type U (e.g., from an entity to a model), and vice versa (from a model to an entity).
